Build the doc
-------------
Before attempting to build the documentation, you should install the python
part of the lpOD project. For more information see the INSTALL file located in
lpod_dir/python/INSTALL.

Then, run the Makefile to build the doc with one of the following target:

  html
  latex
  pdf
  changes
  linkcheck
  release

